author: Trey Alston
title: Kid Cudi Explains A Lot On His Return Solo Outing ‘Leader Of The Delinquents’
description: Kid Cudi has returned with his first solo song in four years. It's 'Leader of the Delinquents' and it clues fans into the ride that he's gone on.
content: Kid Cudi's first solo song in four years is here! It's "Leader of the Delinquents" and this is not a drill; Cudi's in rare form here, rapping, not making melodies, and digging into the entity of Cudi himself. Who is this guy? How has he been? What's he doing … [+2553 chars]
